<body itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/EmailMessage" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; width: 100% !important; height: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; background-color: #f6f6f6; margin: 0;" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">

<table class="body-wrap" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; width: 100%; background-color: #f6f6f6; margin: 0;" bgcolor="#f6f6f6"><tr style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;"><td style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0;" valign="top"></td>
    <td class="container" width="600" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; display: block !important; max-width: 600px !important; clear: both !important; margin: 0 auto;" valign="top">
      <div class="content" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; max-width: 600px; display: block; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <table class="main" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" itemprop="action" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ConfirmAction" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: #fff; margin: 0; border: 1px solid #e9e9e9;" bgcolor="#fff"><tr style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;"><td class="content-wrap" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 20px;" valign="top">
              <meta itemprop="name" content="Confirm Email" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;" /><table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;"><tr style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;" valign="top"><td class="content-block" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 20px;">
                    <%= "#{@student.first_name} #{@student.last_name} (nickname: '#{@student.nickname}')" %>, age <%= "#{@student.age}" %> years, wants to have a Skype partnership with you, <%="#{@volunteer.first_name}" %>. {By the way, Thais often prefer that you use their <b>nickname</b> in normal conversation.}
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr><img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/ccmcoversbsc/at_coffee_shop.jpg" alt="Coffee shop" height="380" width="520" align="middle"/></tr>

                <tr><td class="content-block" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 20px;" valign="top"> 
                    Here is the Skype time slot <%= @student.gender == "male" || @student.gender == "ผู้ชาย" ? "he" : "she" %> has chosen:
                    <ul>
                      <% @skype_time_slots.order("orderday").order("orderam").order("ordertime").each do |slot|%>
                            <li><%= slot.day %> <%= slot.time_period %> <%= slot.am_pm %></li>
                      <% end %>
                    </ul>
                    <p>If <%= @student.nickname %> has chosen a time that is less than 24 hours from the time you have received this email, then your session will start <u>next week</u> -- not this week.</p>

                    <% slot = @skype_time_slots.order("orderday").order("orderam").order("ordertime").first %>

                    <p><%= @student.gender == "male" || @student.gender == "ผู้ชาย" ? "His" : "Her" %> skype address is "<%= @student.skype_name %>".  You can start skyping with <%= @student.gender == "male" || @student.gender == "ผู้ชาย" ? "him" : "her" %> at the time of the scheduled skype time slot you see above (the upcoming...<%= slot.day %> <%= slot.time_period %> <%= slot.am_pm %>).</p>

                    <p><%= @student.gender == "male" || @student.gender == "ผู้ชาย" ? "He" : "She" %> will be expecting your first Skype call then.  If you cannot connect at that time, please send a message on Skype to '<%= @student.nickname %>' at '<%= @student.skype_name %>' (<%= @student.gender == "male" || @student.gender == "ผู้ชาย" ? "His" : "Her" %> Skype address) regarding the best time for your initial Skype contact with <%= @student.gender == "male" || @student.gender == "ผู้ชาย" ? "him" : "her" %>.</p>

                    <p><b>Please keep your message very short and clear.</b>  You can copy/paste this: "I can not meet with you on <%= slot.day_thai %> <%= slot.time_thai %>  this week.  Please meet with me on Skype at the same time next week." (By the way, the time you see in this paste-able message is your Eastern Standard Time converted to Thai time.)</p>

                <p><u>Make sure to set your Skype app's notifications to "on" on both your mobile device and on your computer.</u></p>

                <p>Also, we highly encourage you to become Facebook friends with <%= @student.nickname %>! <%= @student.facebook == "" ? "" : " (Facebook name: #{@student.facebook})" %>  <u>It is very important that you are able to send and receive instant messages between you and <%= @student.nickname %> during the days between each of your Skype conversations, in case one of you needs to postpone the conversation for that week.</u></p>
                <b>We hope you have a great time conversing with <%= "#{@student.nickname}" %>!!</b>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                </table>
          </table><div class="footer" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; width: 100%; clear: both; color: #999; margin: 0; padding: 20px;">
          <table width="100%" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;"><tr style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;"><td class="aligncenter content-block" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: top; color: #999; text-align: center; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 20px;" align="center" valign="top">From the <a href="http://www.cityenglishproject.com" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; color: #999; text-decoration: underline; margin: 0;">&copy; 2017 City English Project</a> in Bangkok, Thailand.</td>
            </tr></table></div></div>
    </td>
    <td style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0;" valign="top"></td>
  </tr></table></body>
